*Data Integration
.It is the process of combining data from multiple sources into a single, unified system.
.Focuses on bringing data together so it can be used for analysis or loading into a data warehouse.

Example:
Merging customer data from MySQL, Excel, and an API into one combined dataset.

*Data Mapping
.It is the process of defining how data fields from one source match or connect to fields in another system.
.Focuses on matching columns, ensuring correct relationships and structure.

Example:
Mapping cust_id (source) → customer_id (target).

